Wohl’s father, attorney David Wohl, says that as a Trump surrogate he was on calls with the 2016 presidential candidate daily.
David Wohl has regularly appeared on cable news networks to promote the president and his policies.
“The real allegations against Mueller would have been ignored … had we not roped the media into attending the press conference,” Wohl said.
In a brief interview, David Wohl said he had daily conference calls with Trump to hone messaging during the campaign.
David Wohl said he called the Los Angeles Police Department to report financial investigators for stalking them.